You will just need to make sure that you are using the following settings in your email application:

Incoming mail server: mail3.gridhost.co.uk
Protocol: IMAP
Authentication: On
Username: Full email address
Password: The corresponding password
Port: 993
SSL: On
SPA: Off

Outgoing mail server: mail3.gridhost.co.uk
Protocol: SMTP
Port: 465
SSL: On
Authentication: On
Authentication: Use same settings as incoming mail server

Please make sure that you have applied these settings in your application and let me know if you experience any further issues afterwards.
